            ', 
                $(function () {
                    $("[id*=chkAll]").bind("click", function () {
                        if ($(this).is(":checked")) {
                            $("[id*=ddl_Desig] input").attr("checked", "checked");
                        } else {
                            $("[id*=ddl_Desig] input").removeAttr("checked");
                        }
                    });
                    $("[id*=ddl_Desig] input").bind("click", function () {
                        if ($("[id*=ddl_Desig] input:checked").length == $("[id*=ddl_Desig] input").length) {
                            $("[id*=chkAll]").attr("checked", "checked");
                        } else {
                            $("[id*=chkAll]").removeAttr("checked");
                        }
                    });
                });
            ',

                function doClick() {
                    PageMethods.Get_Data();

                $(function () {
                    $("[id*=chkAll]").bind("click", function () {
                        if ($(this).is(":checked")) {
                            $("[id*=ddl_Desig] input").attr("checked", "checked");
                        } else {
                            $("[id*=ddl_Desig] input").removeAttr("checked");
                        }
                    });
                    $("[id*=ddl_Desig] input").bind("click", function () {
                        if ($("[id*=ddl_Desig] input:checked").length == $("[id*=ddl_Desig] input").length) {
                            $("[id*=chkAll]").attr("checked", "checked");
                        } else {
                            $("[id*=chkAll]").removeAttr("checked");
                        }
                    });
                });
